item.title: about
item.author: felix.niederwanger@suse.de (phoenix)
item.description: openQA bites is a blog about tutorials, insights and love stories from a humble openQA developer. Its aim is to provide small and biteable posts about typical usage issues that every openQA dev encounters and atypical corner-cases that are worth to be writing down somewhere.
